1 create empty folder name MEARAPP
2 create package.json by using command          npm init -y
3 install express by using command              npm i express
4 created pages by express
installed nodemon by                          npm i nodemon -g   
restart your pc
put all folders in server
apply middleware
create atlas mongodb cluster
inside cluster create db
install mongodb
install mongoose locally in your project          npm i mongoose
for security, installing dotenv